headline: Agoda Launches New Program to Partner with Travel Creators and Drive Bookings
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has launched the Agoda Ambassador program, a new initiative designed to strengthen commercial ties with travel creators on social media. The initiative will see Agoda working directly with travel creators to inspire their audiences to book travel through the platform.
